    "Performance does not increase through including overly specific instructions to correct infrequent mistakes.",
    "Providing the model with example sentences does improve performance, but as evidenced by the lower accuracy of our more elaborate prompt, the information that is presented to the model should be chosen carefully.",
    "Overall, prompts should be concise, but elaborate enough to provide essential instructions.",
    "Second, temperature settings need to be chosen for the prompt.",
    "The responses from ChatGPT are never fully deterministic."
